Great class!  Really fun and interesting!  Lectures are great, and as long as you attend/take notes you don't need to read the book.
 
 As long as you do semi-decent on the exams the class will be an easy A because there is a TON of in-class extra credit.
He's a really nice guy and very funny. Lectures weren't bad, and the test was easy as long as you go to class.
Good teacher, knows his stuff. Tests not too bad as long as you go to lectures and take notes.
This guys knows his stuff but is NOT a good lecturer; has a good sense of humor- nerdy but good, but seriosuly his lectures are pretty boring; tests are not easy; go to class and take good notes
